        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The emphatic tone of the words, “whosoever would, he consecrated him,” possibly indicates that, in spite of all that Jeroboam and his prophet could do, there was some difficulty in securing candidates for his unauthorised priesthood.",
