      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "he consecrated him",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The Hebrew expression is ‘he filled his hand.’ See margin of A.V. The idea is ‘he intrusted this solemn office to his charge.’",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
